# React UI Rules

## Patterns
- Functional components + hooks
- Custom hooks: `use` prefix (`useOrders`, `useSyncStatus`)
- Components: PascalCase files (`OrderScreen.jsx`)
- CSS: Tailwind utilities; classes kebab-case

## i18n (required)
- `react-i18next` with `locales/en.json` and `locales/ar.json`
- No hardcoded user-facing strings
- Menu content: pick `nameEn`/`nameAr` from API based on active locale

## RTL
```jsx
// Set on root when locale === 'ar'
<html dir={locale === 'ar' ? 'rtl' : 'ltr'}>
```
Use logical Tailwind: `ms-4`, `me-4`, `text-start` — not `ml-4`, `text-left`.

## POS-specific
- Touch targets ≥ 48px (`TOUCH_TARGET_SIZE`)
- No animations (`ENABLE_ANIMATIONS=false`)
- Large buttons, simple grid layouts
- Offline banner when disconnected
- Menu grid read-only — no edit controls for staff

## Dashboard
- Recharts for analytics
- Role-scoped data: venue_manager sees own venue only
- Live metrics via `dashboard:metrics_tick` WebSocket

## State
- Server state: fetch + WebSocket updates
- POS order state: local-agent as source of truth during session
